Title: An Eye for an Eye
Plot: When a sailor officer receives a pair of blue eyeballs, the NCIS team starts investigating the case. Gibbs comes on a trace for a past Navy agent that does illegal work.
GuestStars: Anthony Heald, Brian Dietzen, Carlos Lacamara, Madison Mason, Mark Adair-Rios, Cleo King, Daniel Jay Shore, Tania Raymonde
